title.rendered: A&A Associate Wins Prestigious Shams Award for “Top Performing Channel Partner- 2022”

content.rendered: A&A Associate was bestowed with the great honor of the “Top Performing Channel Partner of 2022” by Shams Freezone. We will continue to support and build the UAE business ecosystem through our engagements with small and medium enterprises, as well as large corporations alike. While the UAE was recovering from the crippling effect of the global pandemic, A&A Associate played a significant role in promoting business setup for entrepreneurs in the Sharjah Media City (Shams) Free Zone and was rightly recognized for the same.
